      <txt c="X" a="X" r="X" s="2" w="850" x="40" y="80" delay="0" pt="1" e="-3" align="left">All of the ship’s and crew’s paperwork was in order. Immigration officials asked the Captain for some cans of soda as they will not leave the ship "empty-handed". After long negotiations, the Captain agreed to give them six cans of soda.

How would the cans of soda be considered?</txt>
